title: Graphillion: Kazoeage Oneesan wo Sukue

alternative_titles.ja: Graphillion: 数え上げおねえさんを救

synopsis:
A direct sequel to Fukashigi no Kazoekata commissioned by Graphillion. Graphillion is a Python software package on search, optimization, and enumeration for a very large set of graphs. This video is a quick tutorial to learn what Graphillion is.

(Source: Official YouTube Page)
